            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EThree%20basic%20factors%20contribute%20to%20the%20destruction%20of%20a%20society%2C%20and%20Sodom%20had%20them%20all!%20Sodom%20was%20destroyed%20because%20its%20citizens%20were%20proud%2C%20lazy%2C%20and%20gluttonous.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhen%20a%20people%20become%20proud%2C%20their%20intellects%20excuse%20them%20from%20standards%20of%20basic%20decency.%20The%20Sodomites%20grew%20so%20proud%20and%20arrogant%20that%20they%20thought%20they%20could%20leave%20the%20natural%20order%20of%20sexuality%20and%20engage%20in%20homosexuality.%20God%2C%20however%2C%20viewed%20their%20perverted%20ways%20as%20%22loathsome%22%20(Ezekiel%2016%3A50).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIn%20addition%20to%20being%20proud%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Sodom%20were%20lazy%20and%20unconcerned%20about%20others.%20Being%20so%20self-centered%2C%20they%20had%20little%20to%20do%20with%20their%20time.%20People%20who%20are%20bored%20and%20unconcerned%20about%20others%20gradually%20begin%20to%20live%20for%20pleasure.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EFinally%2C%20the%20inhabitants%20of%20Sodom%20were%20overfed%20gluttons.%20They%20had%20so%20much%20bread%20and%20food%20that%20their%20entire%20lifestyle%20revolved%20around%20eating%20and%20pleasure.%20Though%2C%20of%20course%2C%20we%20need%20food%2C%20it%20is%20never%20to%20be%20the%20focus%20of%20our%20lives.%20As%20Christians%2C%20we%20should%20%22eat%20to%20live%2C%22%20not%20%22live%20to%20eat%22!%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EHow%20can%20we%20guard%20against%20these%20three%20deadly%20diseases%20of%20society%3F%20We%20must%20continually%20humble%20ourselves%20in%20prayer%20before%20God.%20We%20must%20then%20work%20for%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20God%2C%20showing%20concern%20for%20and%20compassion%20to%20others%20and%20not%20just%20living%20for%20pleasure.%20We%20must%20regularly%20fast%20to%20remind%20ourselves%20that%20man%20shall%20not%20live%20by%20bread%20alone.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EPrayer%2C%20godly%20work%2C%20and%20fasting%20are%20the%20%22salt%22%20that%20will%20preserve%20against%20the%20rot%20of%20condemned%20societies%20of%20the%20past.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
