            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Ezekiel.16:42-17:24",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EEzekiel%2016%3A42-17%3A24%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_42%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2242%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E42%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThen%20at%20last%20my%20fury%20against%20you%20will%20be%20spent%2C%20and%20my%20jealous%20anger%20will%20subside.%20I%20will%20be%20calm%20and%20will%20not%20be%20angry%20with%20you%20anymore.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_43%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2243%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E43%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20first%2C%20because%20you%20have%20not%20remembered%20your%20youth%20but%20have%20angered%20me%20by%20doing%20all%20these%20evil%20things%2C%20I%20will%20fully%20repay%20you%20for%20all%20of%20your%20sins%2C%20says%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20For%20you%20have%20added%20lewd%20acts%20to%20all%20your%20detestable%20sins.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_44%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2244%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E44%3C%2Fspan%3EEveryone%20who%20makes%20up%20proverbs%20will%20say%20of%20you%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BLike%20mother%2C%20like%20daughter.%26%23x2019%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_45%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2245%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E45%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20your%20mother%20loathed%20her%20husband%20and%20her%20children%2C%20and%20so%20do%20you.%20And%20you%20are%20exactly%20like%20your%20sisters%2C%20for%20they%20despised%20their%20husbands%20and%20their%20children.%20Truly%20your%20mother%20was%20a%20Hittite%20and%20your%20father%20an%20Amorite.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_46%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2246%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E46%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BYour%20older%20sister%20was%20Samaria%2C%20who%20lived%20with%20her%20daughters%20in%20the%20north.%20Your%20younger%20sister%20was%20Sodom%2C%20who%20lived%20with%20her%20daughters%20in%20the%20south.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_47%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2247%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E47%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20you%20have%20not%20merely%20sinned%20as%20they%20did.%20You%20quickly%20surpassed%20them%20in%20corruption.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_48%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2248%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E48%3C%2Fspan%3EAs%20surely%20as%20I%20live%2C%20says%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20Sodom%20and%20her%20daughters%20were%20never%20as%20wicked%20as%20you%20and%20your%20daughters.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_49%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2249%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E49%3C%2Fspan%3ESodom%26%23x2019%3Bs%20sins%20were%20pride%2C%20gluttony%2C%20and%20laziness%2C%20while%20the%20poor%20and%20needy%20suffered%20outside%20her%20door.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_50%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2250%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E50%3C%2Fspan%3EShe%20was%20proud%20and%20committed%20detestable%20sins%2C%20so%20I%20wiped%20her%20out%2C%20as%20you%20have%20seen.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E16%3A50%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20a%20few%20Hebrew%20manuscripts%20and%20Greek%20version%3B%20Masoretic%20Text%20reads%20%3Cem%3Eas%20I%20have%20seen.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_51%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2251%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E51%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BEven%20Samaria%20did%20not%20commit%20half%20your%20sins.%20You%20have%20done%20far%20more%20detestable%20things%20than%20your%20sisters%20ever%20did.%20They%20seem%20righteous%20compared%20to%20you.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_52%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2252%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E52%3C%2Fspan%3EShame%20on%20you!%20Your%20sins%20are%20so%20terrible%20that%20you%20make%20your%20sisters%20seem%20righteous%2C%20even%20virtuous.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_53%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2253%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E53%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20someday%20I%20will%20restore%20the%20fortunes%20of%20Sodom%20and%20Samaria%2C%20and%20I%20will%20restore%20you%2C%20too.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_54%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2254%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E54%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20you%20will%20be%20truly%20ashamed%20of%20everything%20you%20have%20done%2C%20for%20your%20sins%20make%20them%20feel%20good%20in%20comparison.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_55%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2255%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E55%3C%2Fspan%3EYes%2C%20your%20sisters%2C%20Sodom%20and%20Samaria%2C%20and%20all%20their%20people%20will%20be%20restored%2C%20and%20at%20that%20time%20you%20also%20will%20be%20restored.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_56%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2256%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E56%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20your%20proud%20days%20you%20held%20Sodom%20in%20contempt.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_57%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2257%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E57%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20now%20your%20greater%20wickedness%20has%20been%20exposed%20to%20all%20the%20world%2C%20and%20you%20are%20the%20one%20who%20is%20scorned%26%23x2014%3Bby%20Edom%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E16%3A57%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20many%20Hebrew%20manuscripts%20and%20Syriac%20version%3B%20Masoretic%20Text%20reads%20%3Cem%3EAram.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20all%20her%20neighbors%20and%20by%20Philistia.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_58%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2258%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E58%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20your%20punishment%20for%20all%20your%20lewdness%20and%20detestable%20sins%2C%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_59%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2259%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E59%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BNow%20this%20is%20what%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20I%20will%20give%20you%20what%20you%20deserve%2C%20for%20you%20have%20taken%20your%20solemn%20vows%20lightly%20by%20breaking%20your%20covenant.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_60%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2260%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E60%3C%2Fspan%3EYet%20I%20will%20remember%20the%20covenant%20I%20made%20with%20you%20when%20you%20were%20young%2C%20and%20I%20will%20establish%20an%20everlasting%20covenant%20with%20you.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_61%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2261%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E61%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20you%20will%20remember%20with%20shame%20all%20the%20evil%20you%20have%20done.%20I%20will%20make%20your%20sisters%2C%20Samaria%20and%20Sodom%2C%20to%20be%20your%20daughters%2C%20even%20though%20they%20are%20not%20part%20of%20our%20covenant.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_62%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2262%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E62%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20I%20will%20reaffirm%20my%20covenant%20with%20you%2C%20and%20you%20will%20know%20that%20I%20am%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_16_63%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2263%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E63%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20will%20remember%20your%20sins%20and%20cover%20your%20mouth%20in%20silent%20shame%20when%20I%20forgive%20you%20of%20all%20that%20you%20have%20done.%20I%2C%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20have%20spoken!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_17_1%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEzekiel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EA%20Story%20of%20Two%20Eagles%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20this%20message%20came%20to%20me%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_17_2%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSon%20of%20man%2C%20give%20this%20riddle%2C%20and%20tell%20this%20story%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Israel.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_17_3%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EGive%20them%20this%20message%20from%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BA%20great%20eagle%20with%20broad%20wings%20and%20long%20feathers%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ecovered%20with%20many-colored%20plumage%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet